{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_276531dc8d5f48469a2de184","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t[![Logo](docs/img/Logo.png)](https://ajenti.org/)\n2\t\n3\tAjenti is a Linux & BSD modular server admin panel. Ajenti 2 provides a new interface and a better architecture, developed with [Python3](https://www.python.org/) and [AngularJS](https://angularjs.org/).\n4\t\n5\t<p align=\"center\">\n6\t    <a href=\"https://crowdin.net/project/ajenti\">\n7\t        <img src=\"https://badges.crowdin.net/ajenti/localized.svg\" alt=\"Badge Crowdin\" />\n8\t    </a>\n9\t    <a href=\"https://github.com/ajenti/ajenti/graphs/contributors\">\n10\t        <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/contributors/ajenti/ajenti?label=Contributors\" alt=\"Badge Contributors\" />\n11\t    </a>\n12\t    <a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ajenti/ajenti/master/LICENSE\"> \n13\t        <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/license/ajenti/ajenti?label=License\" alt=\"Badge License\" />\n14\t    </a>\n15\t</p>\n16\t\n17\t----\n18\t\n19\t# Feature highlights\n20\t\n21\t* **Easy installation** : Ajenti 2 can be easy installed [with pip and the provided script](https://docs.ajenti.org/en/latest/man/install.html#installing).\n22\t\n23\t* **Existing configuration** : Picks up your current configuration and works on your existing system as-is, without any preparation.\n24\t\n25\t* **Caring** : Does not overwrite your config files, options and comments. All changes are non-destructive.\n26\t\n27\t* **Batteries included** : Includes lots of plugins for system and software configuration, monitoring and management.\n28\t\n29\t* **Extensible** : Ajenti 2 is easily extensible using Python. Plugin development is a quick and pleasant with Ajenti APIs. [Write your first plugin](https://docs.ajenti.org/en/latest/dev/intro.html#your-first-plugin).\n30\t\n31\t* **Modern** : Pleasant to look at, satisfying to click and accessible anywhere from tablets and mobile.\n32\t\n33\t* **Lightweight** : Small memory footprint and CPU usage. Runs on low-end machines, wall plugs, routers and so on.\n34\t\n35\t----\n36\t\n37\t# Screenshots\n38\t\n39\t<table align=\"center\">\n40\t    <tr>\n41\t        <td align=\"center\">\n42\t            <a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ajenti/ajenti/master/docs/img/rd-login.png\">\n43\t                <img src=\"docs/img/rd-login.png\" alt=\"Screenshot Ajenti Login\" width=\"300px\" />\n44\t            </a>\n45\t        </td>\n46\t        <td align=\"center\">\n47\t            <a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ajenti/ajenti/master/docs/img/rd-dashboard.png\">\n48\t                <img src=\"docs/img/rd-dashboard.png\" alt=\"Screenshot Ajenti Dashboard\" width=\"300px\" /> \n49\t            </a>\n50\t        </td>\n51\t        <td align=\"center\">\n52\t            <a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ajenti/ajenti/master/docs/img/rd-settings.png\"> \n53\t                <img src=\"docs/img/rd-settings.png\" alt=\"Screenshot Ajenti Settings\" width=\"300px\" />\n54\t            </a>\n55\t        </td>\n56\t    </tr>\n57\t    <tr>\n58\t        <td align=\"center\">\n59\t            <a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ajenti/ajenti/master/docs/img/rd-plugins.png\"> \n60\t                <img src=\"docs/img/rd-plugins.png\" alt=\"Screenshot Ajenti Plugins\" width=\"300px\" /> \n61\t            </a>\n62\t        </td>\n63\t        <td align=\"center\">\n64\t            <a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ajenti/ajenti/master/docs/img/rd-systemd.png\"> \n65\t                <img src=\"docs/img/rd-systemd.png\" alt=\"Screenshot Ajenti Systemd\" width=\"300px\" />\n66\t            </a> \n67\t        </td>\n68\t        <td align=\"center\">\n69\t            <a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ajenti/ajenti/master/docs/img/rd-terminal.png\"> \n70\t                <img src=\"docs/img/rd-terminal.png\" alt=\"Screenshot Ajenti Terminal\" width=\"300px\" /> \n71\t            </a>\n72\t        </td>\n73\t    </tr>\n74\t</table>\n75\t\n76\tSee https://docs.ajenti.org for more information\n77\t\n78\t----\n79\t\n80\t# Contributors ✨\n81\t\n82\tThanks goes to these wonderful people ([emoji key](https://allcontributors.org/docs/en/emoji-key)):\n83\t\n84\t<!-- ALL-CONTRIBUTORS-LIST:START - Do not remove or modify this section -->\n85\t<!-- prettier-ignore-start -->\n86\t<!-- markdownlint-disable -->\n87\t<table>\n88\t  <tr>\n89\t    <td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://www.unpeud.info\"><img src=\"https://avatars2.githubusercontent.com/u/10401079?v=4?s=75\" width=\"75px;\" alt=\"\"/><br /><sub><b>Kientz Arnaud</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/ajenti/ajenti/commits?author=kiarn\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n90\t    <td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://github.com/DmZ\"><img src=\"https://avatars2.githubusercontent.com/u/222974?v=4?s=75\" width=\"75px;\" alt=\"\"/><br /><sub><b>Dmitry Zamaruev</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/ajenti/ajenti/commits?author=DmZ\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n91\t    <td align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://dierz.pro\"><img src=\"https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/7171587?v=4?s=75\" width=\"75px;\" alt=\"\"/><br /><sub><b>Ivlev Denis</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/ajenti/ajenti/commits?author=ivlevdenis\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n92\t    <td align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://bryukh.com\"><img src=\"https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/343120?v=4?s=75\" width=\"75px;\" alt=\"\"/><br /><sub><b>Valentin Bryukhanov</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/ajenti/ajenti/commits?author=Bryukh\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n93\t    <td align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://kstep.me\"><img src=\"https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/28537?v=4?s=75\" width=\"75px;\" alt=\"\"/><br /><sub><b>Konstantin Stepanov</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/ajenti/ajenti/commits?author=kstep\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n94\t    <td align=\"center\"><a href=\"ht